      <title>韩国央行仍保留再次维持利率不变的可能性</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-06/bank-of-korea-leaves-door-open-to-another-rate-hold-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国央行行长李昌镛反驳了有关本月晚些时候降息的猜测，他强调财政刺激措施在支撑受到唐纳德·特朗普关税威胁的经济方面发挥的作用。他在东京接受了彭博社 Shery Ahn 的独家采访。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-06/bank-of-korea-leaves-door-open-to-another-rate-hold-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Feb 2025 08:14:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拉脱维亚确认哈萨克斯坦将重返央行行长职位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/latvia-confirms-kazaks-will-return-as-central-bank-governor</link>
      <description><![CDATA[拉脱维亚批准马丁斯·卡扎克斯再次担任央行行长，任期为五年，结束了数月的政治内斗，此前卡扎克斯于 2024 年底卸任且无人继任。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/latvia-confirms-kazaks-will-return-as-central-bank-governor</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Feb 2025 08:04:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Seven & i 财团有望利用美国银行和花旗银行提供收购融资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/seven-i-consortium-said-to-tap-bofa-citi-for-buyout-financing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士称，提议将 Seven &amp; i Holdings Co. 私有化的财团已获得花旗集团和美国银行的融资，从而让参与这项可能破纪录的管理层收购竞标的财团变得更加强大。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/seven-i-consortium-said-to-tap-bofa-citi-for-buyout-financing</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Feb 2025 08:02:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>沙特 IPO 热潮加深股市多元化</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/saudi-ipo-spree-deepens-diversification-in-stock-market</link>
      <description><![CDATA[沙特阿拉伯旨在摆脱经济对石油销售依赖的经济总体规划在一个关键领域显现出来：股票发行。从科技初创公司到金融服务公司，一系列公司纷纷发行股票，使长期以来由银行和石化产品主导的股市变得多元化。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/saudi-ipo-spree-deepens-diversification-in-stock-market</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Feb 2025 08:00:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国央行日：今日决策有何期待</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-06/boe-day-what-to-expect-from-today-s-decision-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[预计英国央行将第三次下调利率至 4.5%，同时下调英国经济增长预期并预测今年通胀率将上升。彭博社的 Lizzy Burden 对此进行了预测。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-06/boe-day-what-to-expect-from-today-s-decision-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Feb 2025 07:51:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着财政部长谈判进入最后阶段，黎巴嫩债券市场恢复上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/lebanon-bond-rally-resumes-as-finmin-talks-enter-final-phase</link>
      <description><![CDATA[交易员和当地政治观察员称，任命财政部长的谈判已进入最后阶段，黎巴嫩违约的主权债券在停滞三周后再次上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/lebanon-bond-rally-resumes-as-finmin-talks-enter-final-phase</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Feb 2025 07:50:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>匈牙利工业下滑，零售业在缓慢走出衰退中停滞不前</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/hungary-industry-slumps-retail-stagnates-in-slow-recession-exit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[匈牙利12月份工业产出萎缩速度快于预期，零售贸易停滞，表明该国摆脱去年经济衰退的进程将较为缓慢。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/hungary-industry-slumps-retail-stagnates-in-slow-recession-exit</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Feb 2025 07:49:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国兴业银行上调盈利目标，计划派发 17 亿欧元股息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/socgen-announces-1-7-billion-investor-payout-as-profit-beats</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国兴业银行宣布去年向投资者支付 17 亿欧元（18 亿美元），因为受法国零售银行业务复苏的推动，第四季度利润超出预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/socgen-announces-1-7-billion-investor-payout-as-profit-beats</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Feb 2025 05:32:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>摩根大通发现关税将在 2025 年加剧市场波动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/tariffs-to-drive-global-markets-in-volatile-2025-jpmorgan-finds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根大通的电子交易调查显示，本周由美国一系列关税公告引发的全球金融市场动荡似乎只是动荡之年的开始。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/tariffs-to-drive-global-markets-in-volatile-2025-jpmorgan-finds</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Feb 2025 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>收益公布后，美国股票和期货上涨：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着财报季最繁忙的一天到来，股市上涨，在没有任何新的贸易紧张局势的情况下，美国国债收益率下降提振了风险情绪。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Feb 2025 22:37:06 GMT</pubDate>
